data.description: Embrace serenity in your private retreat! 2480 sq. ft home nestled on 48.8 Acres. You will be captivated by the seamless blend of elegance and warmth in this 3 bedroom, 2 full bath and 2 half bath home. The airy and spacious Family room has a wood burning fireplace and lots of windows to enjoy the awe-inspiring setting. Gourmet kitchen with charming bistro area, sub-zero refrigerator, slide-out microwave and custom pantry w/ can drops for organization. Oversized primary room has custom tile shower and large walk in closet that is a safe room. Outdoor retreat w/ 33 ft pool, deck with pergolas, creeks, garden area, chicken coop, 30 Amp RV Plug and shop with 400 sq. ft apartment. Property is cross fenced for livestock. The possibilities are endless!
